sequenceDiagram
  actor CEO
  participant Next as Next.js SSR on Cloudflare
  participant API as Fastify on Railway
  participant DB as Railway PostgreSQL
  participant Chat as Contextual Chat

  CEO->>Next: Open /dashboard
  Next->>API: GET /api/dashboard/overview
  API->>DB: Read report snapshots and views
  DB-->>API: Report payloads
  API-->>Next: KPIs, charts, freshness
  Next-->>CEO: Render dashboard
  CEO->>Next: Click Preguntar on chart
  Next->>Chat: Open sidebar with report context
  CEO->>Chat: Ask focused question
  Chat->>API: POST /api/chat/report-question
  API->>API: Use report context first
  API-->>Chat: Answer, warnings, trace_id
